#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwordquiz; is a tool that gives you a powerful way to master new "
"vocabularies. It may be a language or any other kind of terminology."
msgstr ""
"&kwordquiz; je orodje, ki vam omogoča zmogljiv način za obvladovanje novih "
"besedišč. Lahko je jezik ali katera koli druga terminologija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Easy to use"
msgstr "Enostavna za uporabo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &kwordquiz; you build your own vocabulary documents in a simple and "
"intuitive way. The basic layout is a two-column spreadsheet where you type "
"vocabulary entries in one form that you know and in another form that you "
"want to learn. You change the titles of the columns to reflect what you are "
"practicing."
msgstr ""
"Z &kwordquiz; na preprost in intuitiven način sestavite lastne dokumente z "
"besediščem. Osnovna postavitev je preglednica z dvema stolpcema, v katero "
"vnašate vnose besedišča v eni obliki, ki jo poznate, in v drugi obliki, ki "
"se je želite naučiti. Naslove stolpcev spremenite tako, da odražajo, kar "
"vadite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quiz types"
msgstr "Vrste kviza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have entered your vocabulary, you are ready to start a quiz. Maybe "
"you want to start with a flashcard session. Later you can move on to a "
"multiple choice quiz, or do the powerful question and answer quiz. You get "
"instant feedback on correct and incorrect answers, and you have the option "
"to repeat any errors, further improving your learning efficiency. If you "
"need a little extra help you can use the hint function."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete svoj besedišče, ste pripravljeni na začetek kviza. Morda želite "
"začeti s sejo flashcard. Pozneje lahko preidete na kviz z več možnimi "
"izbirami ali rešite zmogljiv kviz z vprašanji in odgovori. Prejmete "
"takojšnje povratne informacije o pravilnih in nepravilnih odgovorih in imate "
"možnost ponoviti morebitne napake, s čimer še izboljšate svojo učno "
"učinkovitost. Če potrebujete malo dodatne pomoči, lahko uporabite funkcijo "
"namigovanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practice modes"
msgstr "Načini vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select how you want to practice. &kwordquiz; offers three different "
"modes to make practicing more efficient. The different modes make it "
"possible to decide which column is used as a question, answer or both. "
"Additionally you can choose whether to use a sequential or random order."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, kako želite vaditi. &kwordquiz; ponuja tri različne načine "
"za učinkovitejšo vadbo. Različni načini omogočajo izbiro, kateri stolpec bo "
"uporabljen kot vprašanje, odgovor ali oboje. Poleg tega lahko izberete, ali "
"želite uporabiti zaporedni ali naključni vrstni red."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary documents"
msgstr "Dokumenti besedišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwordquiz; can open several types of vocabulary data. The default format is "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.kvtml</filename>, a file format shared by "
"several &kde; programs. &kwordquiz; should also open <filename class="
"\"extension\">.wql</filename> files created by &kwordquiz; for &Windows;, "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.csv</filename> files with comma separated "
"text, <ulink url=\"http://www.vokabeln.de/v1/download.htm\"><filename class="
"\"extension\">.voc</filename> files</ulink> created by the old version of "
"Vokabeltrainer, <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/xdxf/files/"
"dicts-XDXF/\"><filename class=\"extension\">.xdxf</filename> files</ulink>, "
"and <filename class=\"extension\">.xml.gz</filename> files created by the "
"old versions of <ulink url=\"http://pauker.sourceforge.net\">Pauker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kwordquiz; lahko odpre več vrst besednih podatkov. Privzeti format je "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.kvtml</filename>, format datoteke, ki si ga "
"deli več &kde; programi. &kwordquiz; prav tako mora odpreti datoteke "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.wql</filename>, ki jih je ustvaril "
"&kwordquiz; za &Windows;, datoteke <filename class=\"extension\">.csv</"
"filename> z besedilom, ločenim z vejicami, <ulink url=\"http://www.vokabeln."
"de/v1/download.htm\"><filename class= \"extension\">.voc</filename> "
"datoteke</ulink>, ustvarjene s staro različico programa Vokabeltrainer, "
"<ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/xdxf/files/dicts-XDXF/"
"\"><filename class=\"extension\">.xdxf</filename> datoteke</ulink> in "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.xml.gz</filename> datoteke, ustvarjene s "
"starimi različicami <ulink url=\"http:/ /pauker.sourceforge.net\">Pauker</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwordquiz; can save your vocabulary documents in several different formats. "
"The default is the <filename class=\"extension\">.kvtml</filename> format "
"used by other &kde; programs. Another available option is comma separated "
"text <filename class=\"extension\">.csv</filename>."
msgstr ""
"&kwordquiz; lahko shrani vaše dokumente besedišča v več različnih formatih. "
"Privzeta je oblika <filename class=\"extension\">.kvtml</filename>, ki jo "
"uporabljajo drugi &kde; programi. Druga razpoložljiva možnost je z vejicami "
"ločeno besedilo <filename class=\"extension\">.csv</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have several files open at the same time, and easily copy or move "
"entries between files."
msgstr ""
"Odprete lahko več datotek hkrati in preprosto kopirate ali premikate vnose "
"med datotekami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Options Menu"
msgstr "Meni z možnostmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menu provides 3 different options for the quiz which are not mutually "
"exclusive."
msgstr ""
"Meni ponuja 3 različne možnosti za kviz, ki se med seboj ne izključujejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menu names will change to reflect the column titles of the currently "
"active vocabulary document. The selected mode will apply to Flashcard, "
"Multiple Choice and Question &amp; Answer."
msgstr ""
"Imena menijev se bodo spremenila tako, da bodo odražala naslove stolpcev "
"trenutno aktivnega dokumenta besedišča. Izbrani način bo veljal za "
"Flashcard, Večkratna izbira in Vprašanja &amp; Odgovor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shuffle</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premešaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During the quiz you will be given the entries in a random order, but each "
"entry will be processed once."
msgstr ""
"Med kvizom boste prejeli vnose v naključnem vrstnem redu, vendar bo vsak "
"vnos obdelan enkrat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Column 1 -&gt; Column 2</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stolpec 1 -&gt; Stolpec 2</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During the quiz you will be given the entries of Column 1 and asked to "
"provide the corresponding Column 2 entries."
msgstr ""
"Med kvizom boste prejeli vnose v 1. stolpcu in morali boste vnesti ustrezne "
"vnose v 2. stolpcu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Mode</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Column 2 -&gt; Column 1</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Način</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stolpec 2 -&gt; Stolpec 1</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During the quiz you will be given the entries of Column 2 and asked to "
"provide the corresponding Column 1 entries."
msgstr ""
"Med kvizom boste prejeli vnose v 2. stolpcu in morali boste vnesti ustrezne "
"vnose v 1. stolpcu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Welcome Page</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pozdravna stran</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When opening KWordQuiz, you will land on the welcome page. This page will "
"list all the previously opened deck. Additionally it lets you create a new "
"deck, open a deck from a file or download deck from the internet. Finally "
"you can also choose which main mode you want to use."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete KWordQuiz, boste pristali na pozdravni strani. Na tej strani bodo "
"navedeni vse predhodno odprte karte. Poleg tega vam omogoča ustvarjanje "
"novega kompleta, odpiranje kompleta iz datoteke ali prenos kompleta iz "
"interneta. Končno lahko izberete tudi, kateri glavni način želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Welcome Page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pozdravna stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Welcome Page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pozdravna stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Vocabulary Editor</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urejevalnik besedišča</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The vocabulary document area has the appearance of a spreadsheet-like grid. "
"The grid consists of cells organized in two columns and a number of rows. "
"Each column and row has a header. The column headers are used to specify the "
"titles of the vocabulary document. They can be set by editing the first row."
msgstr ""
"Območje dokumenta z besediščem je videti kot mreža, podobna preglednici. "
"Mreža je sestavljena iz celic, organiziranih v dveh stolpcih in številnih "
"vrsticah. Vsak stolpec in vrstica ima glavo. Naslovi stolpcev se uporabljajo "
"za določanje naslovov dokumenta besedišča. Nastavite jih lahko z urejanjem "
"prve vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click in a cell of the grid to make it the active cell. You can use "
"the up and down arrow to move up and down in the table and tab to move to "
"the next element."
msgstr ""
"Lahko kliknete celico mreže, da postane aktivna celica. S puščico gor in dol "
"se lahko premikate gor in dol v tabeli in zavihek, da se premaknete na "
"naslednji element."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Vocabulary Editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejevalnik besedišča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Vocabulary Editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejevalnik besedišča</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the document, you build a vocabulary of pair-wise entries in the two "
"columns. You can enter text into the active cell simply by starting to type. "
"The cell will now be in edit mode and you can select all or part of the "
"text. You can also edit a cell by double-clicking it or by pressing "
"<keycap>F2</keycap> and making changes directly in the cell."
msgstr ""
"V dokumentu sestavite besednjak vnosov po parih v dveh stolpcih. Besedilo "
"lahko vnesete v aktivno celico preprosto tako, da začnete tipkati. Celica bo "
"zdaj v načinu za urejanje in lahko izberete celotno ali del besedila. Celico "
"lahko uredite tudi tako, da jo dvokliknete ali pritisnete <keycap>F2</"
"keycap> in spremenite neposredno v celici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have finished typing one entry, press the return key and the next "
"cell will automatically become active. Hence, it's easy to quickly type "
"several entries. There is really no limit to the number of rows you can have "
"in a document."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s tipkanjem enega vnosa, pritisnite tipko za vrnitev in naslednja "
"celica bo samodejno postala aktivna. Zato je enostavno hitro vnesti več "
"vnosov. V resnici ni omejitev glede števila vrstic, ki jih lahko imate v "
"dokumentu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flashcard Session</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seja s kartami</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select Flashcard from the navigation panel to start a flashcard session on "
"the entries of the active vocabulary document. The mode selected in the "
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu> menu will be used. If you change the options "
"during a session, the session will be restarted."
msgstr ""
"Izberite Flashcard na navigacijski plošči, da začnete sejo s kartami na "
"vnosih dokumenta aktivnega besedišča. Uporabljen bo način, izbran v meniju "
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu>. Če med sejo spremenite možnosti, se bo seja "
"znova zagnala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are working with long expressions, the window can be resized to make "
"more space available. The font size will also influence how much will fit in "
"the different parts of the window."
msgstr ""
"Če delate z dolgimi izrazi, lahko spremenite velikost okna, da bo na voljo "
"več prostora. Velikost pisave bo vplivala tudi na to, koliko se bo prilegalo "
"v različne dele okna."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Flashcard Session</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Seja s kartami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Flashcard Session</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seja s kartami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Initially the front of the card is displayed. Use the <guibutton>Check</"
"guibutton> to see the other side."
msgstr ""
"Sprva se prikaže sprednja stran kartice. Uporabite <guibutton>Preveri</"
"guibutton>, da vidite drugo stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move on to the next card, either select <guibutton>I Know</guibutton> to "
"count the card as correct or <guibutton>I Don't Know</guibutton> to count "
"the card as incorrect."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite premakniti na naslednjo kartico, bodisi izberite "
"<guibutton>Vem</guibutton>, da kartico štejete kot pravilno, ali "
"<guibutton>Ne vem</guibutton>, da kartico štejete kot napačno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237 index.docbook:276 index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guibutton>Repeat Errors</guibutton> to repeat the cards you have "
"counted as incorrect."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guibutton>Ponovi napake</guibutton>, če želite ponoviti karte, ki "
"ste jih šteli kot nepravilne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240 index.docbook:279 index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guibutton>Try again</guibutton> to start the session from the "
"beginning again. If you are using a random mode the cards will be reshuffled."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guibutton>Poskusi znova</guibutton>, da znova začnete sejo od "
"začetka. Če uporabljate naključni način, bodo karte premešane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score section at the top of the screen shows the number of cards, the "
"number of cards you have seen, the number of cards counted as correct, and "
"the number counted as incorrect."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek z rezultati na vrhu zaslona prikazuje število kart, število kart, "
"ki ste jih videli, število kart, ki so bile preštete kot pravilne, in "
"številke, ki so bile preštete kot nepravilne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Multiple Choice Session</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seja z več možnostmi</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select Multiple Choice in the welcome page to start a multiple choice quiz "
"on the entries in the active vocabulary document. The mode selected in the "
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu> menu will be used. If you change options during a "
"session, the session will be restarted."
msgstr ""
"Izberite Več možnosti na pozdravni strani, da začnete kviz z več izbirami o "
"vnosih v dokumentu aktivnega besedišča. Uporabljen bo način, izbran v meniju "
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu>. Če med sejo spremenite možnosti, se bo seja "
"znova zagnala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are working with long expressions the window can be resized to make "
"more room. The font size (selected for the editor) will also influence how "
"much will fit in the different parts of the window."
msgstr ""
"Če delate z dolgimi izrazi, lahko spremenite velikost okna, da naredite več "
"prostora. Velikost pisave (izbrana za urejevalnik) bo prav tako vplivala na "
"to, koliko se bo prilegalo v različne dele okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the example below the user gave an incorrect answer to the previous "
"question. He/she is now about to answer the next question."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem primeru je uporabnik na prejšnje vprašanje dal napačen odgovor. "
"Zdaj bo odgovoril na naslednje vprašanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Multiple Choice Session</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Seja z več možnostmi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Choice Session</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seja z več možnostmi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your choices are shown on the middle of the screen. Select the one you think "
"is correct. Use <guibutton>Check</guibutton> to see if the answer is "
"correct. If you have activated the automatic mode in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu></menuchoice> your selection is "
"checked immediately."
msgstr ""
"Vaše izbire so prikazane na sredini zaslona. Izberite tistega, ki se vam zdi "
"pravilen. Če želite preveriti, ali je odgovor pravilen, uporabite "
"<guibutton>Preveri</guibutton>. Če ste aktivirali samodejni način v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu></menuchoice>, je vaša izbira takoj "
"označena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282 index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score section at the top of the screen shows the number of questions, "
"the number of questions you have answered, the number of correct answers, "
"and the number of incorrect answers."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek z rezultati na vrhu zaslona prikazuje število vprašanj, število "
"vprašanj, na katera ste odgovorili, število pravilnih odgovorov in število "
"nepravilnih odgovorov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Question &amp; Answer Session</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seja vprašanj &amp; odgovorov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select Question &amp; Answer from the navigation panel to start a question "
"&amp; answer session on the entries in the active vocabulary. The mode "
"selected in the <guimenu>Mode</guimenu> menu will be used. If you change "
"mode during a session, the session will be restarted."
msgstr ""
"Izberite vprašanje &amp; Odgovorite na navigacijski plošči, da začnete "
"vprašanje &amp; odgovor na vnose v aktivnem besedišču. Uporabljen bo način, "
"izbran v meniju <guimenu>Način</guimenu>. Če med sejo spremenite način, se "
"bo seja znova zagnala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are working with long expressions, the window can be resized to make "
"more room. The font size (selected for the editor) will also influence how "
"much will fit in the different parts of the window."
msgstr ""
"Če delate z dolgimi izrazi, lahko spremenite velikost okna, da naredite več "
"prostora. Velikost pisave (izbrana za urejevalnik) bo prav tako vplivala na "
"to, koliko se bo prilegalo v različne dele okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the example below the user gave a correct answer to the previous question "
"(to see how incorrect answers are handled, see the <link linkend=\"multiple"
"\">Multiple Choice</link> chapter). He/she is now about to answer the next "
"question."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem primeru je uporabnik pravilno odgovoril na prejšnje vprašanje (če "
"si želite ogledati, kako se obravnavajo nepravilni odgovori, glejte poglavje "
"<link linkend=\"multiple\">Večkratna izbira</link>). Zdaj bo odgovoril na "
"naslednje vprašanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Question &amp; Answer Session</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Seja vprašanje &amp; odgovor</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Question &amp; Answer Session</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seja vprašanje &amp; odgovor</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your question is shown on the center. Type your answer in the edit field. "
"Use <guibutton>Check</guibutton> or &Enter; to see if the answer is correct."
msgstr ""
"Vaše vprašanje je prikazano na sredini. Vnesite odgovor v polje za urejanje. "
"Uporabite <guibutton>Preveri</guibutton> ali &Enter; da vidite, ali je "
"odgovor pravilen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> to get the next correct letter of the "
"answer. In <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu></menuchoice> you may "
"choose to count any questions where you use the hint function as incorrect."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guibutton>Namig</guibutton>, da dobite naslednjo pravilno črko "
"odgovora. V <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu></menuchoice> lahko "
"izberete, da vsa vprašanja, pri katerih uporabljate funkcijo namigovanja, "
"štejete kot nepravilna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fill-in-the-blank"
msgstr "Izpolni prazna polja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"'Fill-in-the-blank' is a powerful way to practice in &kwordquiz;. It is a "
"special kind of question and answer quiz that needs to be described in more "
"detail."
msgstr ""
"'Izpolni prazna polja' je zmogljiv način za vadbo v &kwordquiz;. Gre za "
"posebno vrsto kviza vprašanj in odgovorov, ki ga je treba podrobneje opisati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consider the following table. It could be a vocabulary in &kwordquiz;:"
msgstr "Razmislite o naslednji tabeli. Lahko bi bil besednjak v &kwordquiz;:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "English"
msgstr "angleščina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "German"
msgstr "nemščina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>1</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>1</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:352 index.docbook:358 index.docbook:364 index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "We own a computer"
msgstr "Imamo računalnik"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wir besitzen einen Computer"
msgstr "Wir besitzen einen Computer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>2</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>2</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wir [besitzen] einen Computer"
msgstr "Wir [besitzen] einen Computer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>3</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>3</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wir [besitzen einen] Computer"
msgstr "Wir [besitzen einen] Computer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>4</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>4</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wir [besitzen] einen [Computer]"
msgstr "Wir [besitzen] einen [Computer]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The important thing to note is the placement of the brackets. They tell "
"&kwordquiz; how the quiz should be performed."
msgstr ""
"Pomembna stvar, na katero morate biti pozorni, je namestitev oklepajev. "
"Pravijo &kwordquiz; kako naj se kviz izvede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In 1. there are no brackets. Assuming English is the question and German the "
"answer you have to give the entire expression 'Wir besitzen einen Computer' "
"for a correct answer."
msgstr ""
"V 1. ni oklepajev. Če predpostavimo, da je vprašanje angleščina, odgovor pa "
"nemščina, morate za pravilen odgovor dati celoten izraz 'Wir besitzen einen "
"Computer'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In 2. &kwordquiz; would display the question but also 'Wir ........ einen "
"Computer'. For a correct answer it is sufficient to write 'besitzen'."
msgstr ""
"V 2. &kwordquiz; bi prikazal vprašanje, ampak tudi \"Wir ........ einen "
"Computer\". Za pravilen odgovor zadostuje, da napišete 'besitzen'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"3. shows that a blank can consist of more than one word. The correct answer "
"is 'besitzen einen'."
msgstr ""
"3. kaže, da lahko praznina sestoji iz več kot ene besede. Pravilen odgovor "
"je 'besitzen einen'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In 4. there are two separate blanks. To specify that in the answer you have "
"to write 'besitzen; Computer', &ie; separate the blanks with a semicolon in "
"order to get a correct answer."
msgstr ""
"V 4. sta dve ločeni praznini. Če želite določiti, da morate v odgovor "
"napisati 'besitzen; Computer', &ie; ločite prazna mesta s podpičjem, da "
"dobite pravilen odgovor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Marked blanks are only of relevance if they appear in the answer. Otherwise "
"the brackets are ignored. Furthermore, brackets have no effect in multiple "
"choice quizzes. To simplify the creation of 'Fill-in-the-blank' vocabularies "
"there are menu commands to mark and unmark blanks. Of course you can also "
"just type the brackets. &kwordquiz; checks the syntax. If the text appears "
"in red there is something wrong with the brackets and a quiz cannot be "
"started."
msgstr ""
"Označena prazna polja so pomembna le, če se pojavijo v odgovoru. V "
"nasprotnem primeru se oklepaji ne upoštevajo. Poleg tega oklepaji nimajo "
"učinka pri kvizih z več izbirami. Za poenostavitev ustvarjanja besednjakov "
"za izpolnjevanje praznin obstajajo menijski ukazi za označevanje in "
"odznačevanje praznin. Seveda lahko tudi samo vtipkate oklepaje. &kwordquiz; "
"preveri sintakso. Če je besedilo rdeče, je nekaj narobe z oklepaji in kviza "
"ni mogoče začeti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Tiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwordquiz; provides the ability to print vocabulary documents in several "
"different ways. The printing options are available in the &kwordquiz; "
"editor. When selecting <guibutton>Print...</guibutton> you are presented "
"with a menu where you can select to print the document as a vocabulary list "
"(&ie; as displayed in the editor), a vocabulary exam, or as flashcards. Once "
"the mode is selected, you will be presented with the standard &kde; print "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kwordquiz; omogoča tiskanje dokumentov besedišča na več različnih načinov. "
"Možnosti tiskanja so na voljo v urejevalniku &kwordquiz;. Ko izberete "
"<guibutton>Natisni...</guibutton>, se prikaže meni, kjer lahko izberete "
"tiskanje dokumenta kot seznam besedišča (&ie; kot je prikazan v "
"urejevalniku), izpitu iz besedišča ali kot kartice. Ko je način izbran, se "
"vam prikaže standardno &kde; pogovorno okno za tiskanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Vocabulary Printing Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti tiskanja besedišča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Vocabulary Printing Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti tiskanja besedišča</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary list"
msgstr "Seznam besedišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The vocabulary will be printed as displayed in the editor. This includes "
"font, row heights, and column widths. Make sure that the columns are narrow "
"enough to fit on the page."
msgstr ""
"Besedišče bo natisnjeno, kot je prikazano v urejevalniku. To vključuje "
"pisavo, višino vrstic in širino stolpcev. Prepričajte se, da so stolpci "
"dovolj ozki, da se prilegajo strani."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Print Vocabulary List</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Natisni seznam besedišča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Print Vocabulary List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Natisni seznam besedišča</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary exam"
msgstr "Izpit iz besedišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The vocabulary will be printed as displayed in the editor, except that the "
"right column will be left empty and a third column for scoring is added. "
"Settings used include font, row heights, and column widths. Make sure that "
"the columns are narrow enough to fit on the page."
msgstr ""
"Besedišče bo natisnjeno, kot je prikazano v urejevalniku, le da bo desni "
"stolpec ostal prazen, dodan pa bo tretji stolpec za točkovanje. Uporabljene "
"nastavitve vključujejo pisavo, višine vrstic in širine stolpcev. Prepričajte "
"se, da so stolpci dovolj ozki, da se prilegajo strani."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Print Vocabulary Exam</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Natisni izpit iz besedišča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Print Vocabulary Exam</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Natisni izpit iz besedišča</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flashcards"
msgstr "Kartice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two 3\" x 5\" cards per page. The cards will always be printed in landscape."
msgstr ""
"Dve kartici velikosti 3\" x 5\" na stran. Kartice bodo vedno natisnjene "
"ležeče."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Print Flashcards</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Natisni kartice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Print Flashcards</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Natisni kartice</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialogs"
msgstr "Pogovorna okna"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General Settings</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošne nastavitve</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>General Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Splošne nastavitve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošne nastavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select what type of session a newly opened vocabulary should start "
"in. Going directly to a quiz can prevent you from seeing any entries in "
"advance."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, v kateri vrsti seje naj se začne na novo odprti besednjak. "
"Če greste neposredno na kviz, lahko preprečite, da bi vnaprej videli "
"kakršnekoli vnose."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For all sessions you can select if the scores should be displayed as "
"percentages instead of absolute numbers."
msgstr ""
"Za vse seje lahko izberete, ali naj bodo rezultati prikazani v odstotkih "
"namesto v absolutnih številkah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that the settings are automatically applied."
msgstr "Upoštevajte, da se nastavitve samodejno uporabijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Column Settings</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nastavitve stolpca</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can open this dialog from the editor."
msgstr "To pogovorno okno lahko odprete v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Column Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve stolpca</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Column Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve stolpca</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this dialog to define the column titles and column languages. Click on a "
"language to selected it or close the dialog to discard any changes."
msgstr ""
"S tem pogovornim oknom določite naslove stolpcev in jezike stolpcev. "
"Kliknite na jezik, da ga izberete, ali zaprite pogovorno okno, da zavržete "
"vse spremembe."

